      <title>thread用法</title>
      <link href="/2025/07/03/C++%E2%80%94%E2%80%94thread%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>/2025/07/03/C++%E2%80%94%E2%80%94thread%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="thread用法"><a href="#thread用法" class="headerlink" title="thread用法"></a>thread用法</h1><h2 id="thread构造"><a href="#thread构造" class="headerlink" title="thread构造"></a>thread构造</h2><p>首先对于thread的构造函数参数的认识：</p><p>在thread构造完成后会立即执行函数</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">test01</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 普通函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t1</span><span class="params">(do_work, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">20</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 匿名函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t2</span><span class="params">([]()&#123;&#125;)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 函数对象</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t6</span><span class="params">(Task(), <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">20</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 成员函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    MyTask task;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 普通成员函数后第一个参数必须时对象或者对象指针</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t3</span><span class="params">(&amp;MyTask::task1, task, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">20</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t4</span><span class="params">(&amp;MyTask::task1, &amp;task, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">20</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 静态成员函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t5</span><span class="params">(&amp;MyTask::task2, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">20</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="thread成员函数"><a href="#thread成员函数" class="headerlink" title="thread成员函数"></a>thread成员函数</h2><p>先理解一个概念，当线程一旦创建，会立即执行，代码的执行也就会开另外的路径，现在就纯在于一个问题？</p><p>调用线程（就是创建子线程的线程）需不需要等待子线程完成（可能需要完成的结果）</p><p>通过join()和detach()成员函数，需要根据具体情况进行分析</p><p>线程创建必须调用join或者detach，不然会报错，因为有这样的判断函数joinable()，且在在析构函数中存在 </p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">test02</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function">std::thread <span class="title">t</span><span class="params">([]()&#123;&#125;)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 阻塞当前线程，等到子线程执行完毕，继续向下执行</span></span><br><span class="line">    t.<span class="built_in">join</span>();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 子线程从当前线程分离，独立运行、调用线程不需要等待</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// t.detach()</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 获得线程编号</span></span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; t.<span class="built_in">get_id</span>() &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 系统最大并发数（cpu核心数）</span></span><br><span class="line">    std::cout &lt;&lt; t.<span class="built_in">hardware_concurrency</span>() &lt;&lt; std::endl;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="参数传递"><a href="#参数传递" class="headerlink" title="参数传递"></a>参数传递</h2><p>构建thread对象的时候，经常使用ref来传递参数，为什么要这么写，有什么好处？</p><ol><li>了解thread内部如何处理传递进来的参数</li><li>了解thread不同传递参数的方式的区别</li><li>了解thread可调用对象的参数类型如何写</li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 笔记 </category>
          
      </categories>
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> C++ </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
